[-] Jackals 2 pieces. They are the same, but at 4th level each has a unique ability.
[1] "Healing": out of combat, quickly regenerates health up to 50% of the maximum.
[1] "Haste": dealing damage, (20-40)% chance - on yourself "Haste" (5) for 10 sec.
[2] Dementia: Dealing damage, (20-50)% chance - Dementia for 7 sec.
[3] "Rage": dealing damage, (10-20)% chance - on yourself "Increase Strength" (300) for 6 sec.
[4-1] Paralyze: Damage, (5-10)% chance - Paralyze for 4 sec.
[4-2] "Weakening": dealing damage, (10-15)% chance - "Weakening" (130) for 33 sec.